ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"日日都係訓醒入錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98387ed8c1aed7cf8acaf1970daa202085c6de0a","tid":627523,"uid":17266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有料洗鬼賣料咩，自己賭唔好？輸左又要比人屌，比人屌都要賣，為乜姐？咪你果份會費囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔撚洗做，有人送錢比你賭，每日channel upload幾張飛講幾句野就有錢收，咁既人都支持，真係去驗下腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人話佢d「會員」都好勁，首先都唔撚講果d係狗定會員，個個都出水你係咪跟曬？贏左藍哥實話同盟會又贏，輸左會點？咪話要跟足佢方法，或者唔好輸打贏要囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講佢d贏錢飛，賭齡有返咁上下，除非你真係黑到仆街，邊個無一兩張贏大錢既飛啊？（佢d贏錢飛其實最多咪又係盤話關😂贏6，7千）你肯定份會後會再遇到？就算真係遇到，夠唔夠補返輸左果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係補到啦，咁一個月回報又係咪真係值比一千一個月？每個月贏一千交會費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲要有返咁上下本去頂住輸果d日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完咁多資料，你都係要入會，或者續會，我只能祝福你，不過如果你班狗自己衰唔夠仲要貼飛引鳩人入會，咁我就一定追鳩擊你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有10日今期就完，大家睇下藍哥點幫大家追數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a739f23bfff7706791be793ab05e816c08ff58","tid":627523,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3166bd92ecf4e8eaa760b4da88d11f6bb26231d1","tid":627523,"uid":36499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd99c0fa2e01138a4cb356dfd389b0059e04097","tid"